Package repast.simphony.parameter

Interface ParameterSweeper

All Superinterfaces:
ParameterSetter
All Known Implementing Classes:
OptimizedParameterSweeper, ParameterTreeSweeper
public interface ParameterSweeper extends ParameterSetter
An interface representing an object that will perform a sweep of a parameter space represented by a series of ParameterSetters.
Author:
Jerry Vos
